These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, bellflower
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, sudoku
2 different games are played: poker, go
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, western
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, pakistani
There 2 different types of food: cucumber, nectarine
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, hip-hop
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1
2. the person playing go is on the far right##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person eating cucumber is the pakistani##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
6. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Flower      | bellflower     | begonia       |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | sudoku     |
| Game           | poker | go   |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | superhero  |
| Nationality   | pakistani | indonesian |
| Food           | cucumber      | nectarine     |
| Music-Genre     | hip-hop    | pop   |

