.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, poppy
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, bluemaster
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, r&b
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, german
There are 2 different favourite colors: white, orange
City: hamburg, paris
1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
2. the person who likes orange is the person traveling to paris##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the fan of indie##1
4. the german is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk    | iced-tea |
| Flower         | poppy        | bellflower  |
| Cigar           | game | bluemaster  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b            | indie    |
| Nationality   | australian     | german   |
| Color           | white         | orange    |
| City     | hamburg           | paris      |

